answers.title:
```rust
for c in text.chars() {
    if let Some(count) = &mut counts.get(&c) {
        counts.insert(c, *count + 1);
    } else {
        counts.insert(c, 1);
    };
}
```

```rust
for c in text.chars() {
    let count = counts.entry(c).or_insert(0);
    *count += 1;
}
```

